-- =============================================================================
-- S17. FMEA (Failure Modes with RPN scoring)
-- =============================================================================
--
-- | # | Failure Mode              | S | O | D | RPN | Rule                    | Playbook                     |
-- |---|---------------------------|---|---|---|-----|-------------------------|------------------------------|
-- | 1 | Telegram token expired    | 7 | 4 | 3 | 84  | SimulatorModeRedirect   | Refresh token in Smriti      |
-- | 2 | LLM inference timeout     | 5 | 6 | 2 | 60  | LlmTimeoutFallback      | Fallback to rule-based       |
-- | 3 | Zenoh session lost        | 9 | 2 | 2 | 36  | ZenohSessionAlive       | Reconnect with backoff       |
-- | 4 | GChat subscription 404    | 7 | 3 | 2 | 42  | GChatPubSub.preflight   | Halt polling, notify operator |
-- | 5 | Offset not persisted      | 8 | 1 | 3 | 24  | OffsetPersisted         | Replay from last known       |
-- | 6 | Rate limit false positive | 4 | 3 | 5 | 60  | RapidFireRateLimit      | Widen window or increase N   |
-- | 7 | Simulator port conflict   | 3 | 2 | 2 | 12  | SimulatorAPI            | Use alternative port         |
-- | 8 | Malformed intent JSON     | 6 | 4 | 3 | 72  | CortexEngine            | Log warning, skip message    |
-- | 9 | All channels unconfigured | 8 | 1 | 1 | 8   | GatewayDispatcher       | Mock mode (no sends)         |
-- |10 | WhatsApp API rate limit   | 5 | 5 | 4 |100  | GatewayDispatcher       | Exponential backoff          |
-- |11 | Smriti DB locked          | 7 | 2 | 3 | 42  | OffsetPersistence       | WAL mode, retry              |
-- |12 | Cortex OOM                | 9 | 1 | 2 | 18  | CortexEngine            | Memory limit + restart       |

